('73661','25539','5','Newly built, state-of-the-art villa with stunning sea views in Cala Llamp / Port d''Andratx'),
('73662','25540','5','Cala Llamp is situated just 2 kilometers away from the luxury marina of Port d''Andratx. The newly built modern style villa sits gloriously on a 1,900 m² west facing hillside plot and enjoys fantastic sea views. The German builder selected only first-class materials and attached great importance to a superior quality of construction.\r\nThe building area of approx. 1,330 m² is divided into the main house, guest house and a separate guest apartment.\r\nThe main house has 2 floors, the upper floor consists of two equal-sized bedrooms, each with dressing room, en suite bathrooms and terrace, on the ground floor are the living-dining room, modern fitted kitchen, tempered wine cellar, bathroom and bedroom with en suite bathroom.\r\nThe guest house offers 2 bedrooms, each with bathroom en suite. Between the main house and the guest house is located the swimming pool (5.5 m x 10 m), a Jacuzzi, a summer kitchen, covered terrace and a spa area with sauna (Klaf), several showers and a fitness room. The 65 m² guest apartment comprises of a living room, kitchen, bedroom and bathroom.\r\nQuality materials have been used throughout, complimented by the use of top of the range installations, luxury fittings & intelligent technical systems such as aluminum / wood sliding panoramic windows with electric blinds, 4 fireplaces (including 3 gas fireplaces), air conditioning, under floor heating (heat pump), installed music system from simple audio / B & W, TVs in all bedrooms (Loewe), full home automation system from Gira (can be operated also via iPhone / iPad), alarm system and many more. Complete specifications are available on request.'),
